<p>梁恒源针线活样样精通。　蒋雪林 摄 </p>
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200914/cd6c8fd1d5c942d68b6248bde8eb5dd7.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
